Hello everybody! I'm back! 
KSLawdogg told what is happening and I think i am glad i had the break.
I will now be reclaiming my characters once I find out where they currently 
are. That includes the characters that i did not issue that JP3884 controlled.
JP3884, throughout this rpg you have been one of the strongest rule 
enforcers. One of the rules is you can't control anyone else's characters 
unless they say you can. The reason I didnot give out Inferno and company is 
because nothing really big was happening with them. Next I go and don't issue 
out characters please do not take them for yourself even if you desperately 
want them. 

Next time I won't be this nice.........
